{"id": "1001410", "question": "plt.plot作图，隐藏坐标轴", "description": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10\"><p>用plt.plot作图怎么可以让坐标轴隐藏，或者去掉不显示？</p><pre><code class=\"python\">plt.plot(a, b)\r\nplt.show()</code></pre><p><img data-filename=\"sq (1).png\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"width: 50%;\"/></p><p>比如上面这个图是有坐标轴的，我是想去掉坐标轴</p><p><br/></p></div>", "viewer": 14140, "tags": ["统计/机器学习", "数据可视化", "Python"], "answers": [{"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>off一下就关掉了</p><pre><code class=\"python\">plt.plot(a, b)\r\nplt.axis('off')\r\nplt.show()</code></pre><p><br/></p></div>", "lvl2_answer": []}]}